README:

ADD THE FOLDER SLIDERDIRECTIVE TO YOUR PROJECT


SITE THE FOLLOWING IN YOUR HTML: 

<!-- CAROSELL -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="sliderDirective/Carousel.css">
    
    <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.8.2.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="sliderDirective/jquery.carouFredSel-6.0.4-packed.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="sliderDirective/Carousel.js"></script>
    <script src="sliderDirective/sliderDirective/sliderDir.js" type="text/javascript"></script>


ADD DIRECTIVE:


<!-- DIRECTIVE -->
    <div slider-directive data="data" class="sliderDir"></div>


